text: Patriarch Maximus II or Patriarch Maximos II may refer to: * Maximus II of Antioch, Patriarch in 449–455 * Maximus II of Constantinople, Ecumenical Patriarch in 1216 * Maximos II Hakim, Patriarch of the Melkite Greek Catholic Church in 1760–1761 ==See also== * Patriarch (disambiguation) * Maximus (disambiguation) * Patriarch Maximus I (disambiguation)
title: Patriarch Maximus II
